		<fibo-actus-act:hasParameterMapping>Starting from leg 2 of a swap, fibo-fnd-acc-cur:hasNotionalAmount fibo-fnd-acc-cur:MonetaryAmount; fibo-fnd-acc-cur:hasAmount xsd:decimal</fibo-actus-act:hasParameterMapping>
